<h2>Gordon's Fizz</h2>

<div>
  <h3>Ingredients</h3>
  
  <ul>
    <li>Ice</li?>
    <li>25ml Gin</li>
    <li>Sparkling White Wine</li>
    <li>Lemon rind</li>
  </ul>
</div>

<div>
  <h3>Method</h3>
  
  <ul>
    <li>Add ice to champagne glass</li>
    <li>Add gin</li>
    <li>Top up with wine</li>
    <li>Garnish with lemon rind</li>
  </ul>
<div>

Link to this recipe: http://jsrn.net/tablecloth/#cocktails/gordonfizz